ly be obtanied with explosions. But it can also be crafted with nettherite scrap, gold, and redstone.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Current Weapons:</p>\n<p>Australium Frying Pan</p>\n<p>- 15 damge</p>\n<p>- 1 attack speed</p>\n<p>- ignites enemies for 50 seconds</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>",
